              "raw": "{{base_url}}/batches",
              "host": [
                "{{base_url}}"
              ],
              "path": [
                "batches"
              ]
            },
            "description": "Creates a new supply batch linking a farmer to a produce item.\n\nRequest Body:\n\n- farmerId (string, required): MongoDB ID of the farmer\n    \n- produceId (string, required): MongoDB ID of the produce\n    \n- quantity (number, required): Quantity in the batch\n    \n- harvestDate (date, required): Date of harvest\n    \n- status (string, required): pending | shipped | delivered\n    \n\nExample Request:  \n{  \n\"farmerId\": \"69c365e505b...\",  \n\"produceId\": \"69c365f105b...\",  \n\"quantity\": 100,  \n\"harvestDate\": \"2026-03-25\",  \n\"status\": \"pending\"  \n}\n\nResponses:\n\n- 201: Batch created successfully\n    \n- 400: Missing required fields\n    \n- 500: Internal server error"
          },
          "response": []
        },
